config-mysql 
zabbix.conf.php 

Also, take a look at zabbix.sh to understand NUYVM's Zabbix automation 

#######################################################################################

Please, download zabbix.sh to your machine and make it executable 
Do sh zabbix.sh 

Login to your Zabbix server by your browser with user Admin and password zabbix
Don't forget to change this password! 


